<subsection xml:id="subsec-area-of-a-parallelogram-and-rhombus">
    <title>Area of a parallelogram and rhombus</title>
    <p>
       <m>\textbf{Area of a parallelogram}</m> 
    </p>
    <p>
        <ul>
          <li>
            <p>
              Rectangle is a type of parallelogram where all the angles are 90째
            </p>
          </li>
          <li>
            <p>
              All rectangles are parallelograms, but not all parallelograms are rectangles.
            </p>
          </li>
        </ul>
    </p>
    <p>
    <md>
        <mrow>\text{Area of a parallelogram} = \amp \text{base} \times \text{height}</mrow>
        <mrow>= \amp bh </mrow>
    </md>
    </p>
