        <p>
        What is the area of the piece of land?
        </p>
    </statement>
    <solution>
        <p>
        <md>
            <mrow> \text{Area of a parallelogram}=\amp \text{base length} \times \text{Perpendicular height}</mrow>
            <mrow> =\amp 120\,m \times 40\,m</mrow>
            <mrow> =\amp 4\,800\,m^2 </mrow>
        </md>
        </p>
        <p>
        The area of the piece of land is <m>4\,800\,m^2</m>.
        </p>
    </solution>

